{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 5",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-600511340716491339 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/j0rgbv-09/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=600495993187730277&sectionId=600511340716491339)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnK2SI3GX3_text","label":"ggnK2SI3GX3_text","default":"What men are saying about their necks:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTEedFjFHl_text","label":"ggTEedFjFHl_text","default":"<p>\"At 60, my neck skin had relaxed considerably. I was embarrassed to wear open collars. After two months with Omnis, my neck skin is finally firm and toned again. I had feared the retinol because of my sensitive skin—but I had zero problems. My wife noticed before I did.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj-qf2GbiX_text","label":"ggj-qf2GbiX_text","default":"<p><strong>Sergio, 60</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6axwv249b_text","label":"gg6axwv249b_text","default":"<p>At 54, a sporty but smoking man... my face showed its signs. After about 20 days I started seeing more toned and even skin. By week 8, the sagging along my jawline was noticeably reduced. I waited 40 days to write this review because I wanted to be certain. I'm certain.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggx1yAL80aD_text","label":"ggx1yAL80aD_text","default":"<p><strong>Davide S., 54</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggP7455ZqCd_text","label":"ggP7455ZqCd_text","default":"<p>\"The picture is proof your product works on my 64-year-old face and neck after 2 months use! My collar fits differently now. I don't avoid mirrors anymore.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWh3Q5Ge9p_text","label":"ggWh3Q5Ge9p_text","default":"<p><strong>Giovanni P., 64</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzGnRdJ-dv_text","label":"ggzGnRdJ-dv_text","default":"<p>\"I waited months before buying because I thought it was just another advertising scam. I had tried beef tallow, drugstore creams, even an expensive treatment that cost me €300. Nothing worked on my neck. Finally, real advertising and a product that exceeds expectations. The publicity turned out true.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1yQzRutTJ_text","label":"gg1yQzRutTJ_text","default":"<p><strong>Cristiano</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5C2Zi5QvO_text","label":"gg5C2Zi5QvO_text","default":"<p>\"Super hydrating, absorbs easily, doesn't leave that greasy feeling I hated from other products. But the real change was structural—my neck looks tighter, more defined. My barber asked what I was doing differently.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvxU3sNQwk_text","label":"ggvxU3sNQwk_text","default":"<p><strong>Antonio</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj9p67_rhZ_text","label":"ggj9p67_rhZ_text","default":"Recently, Omnis became available in America."},{"type":"html","id":"ggxmZhnIjNF_text","label":"ggxmZhnIjNF_text","default":"<p>For years, this formulation was only available in European pharmacies. American men who discovered it would buy extra jars whenever they traveled to Italy, or have relatives ship it to them.</p><p><br>Six months ago, the laboratory secured distribution in the United States. And the response from American men has been... significant.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggatAuf9G2Y_text","label":"ggatAuf9G2Y_text","default":"<p>\"After spending hundreds on beef tallow creams and every 'men's face cream' I saw advertised on Facebook, this is the first thing that actually works. What beef tallow promised, Omnis actually delivered. My neck is tighter. My jawline is more defined. I'm not invisible anymore.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmEUNL5rAC_text","label":"ggmEUNL5rAC_text","default":"<p><strong>Luca V., New York</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSlhkCwNVA_text","label":"ggSlhkCwNVA_text","default":"<p>\"This product is a game-changer, no joke. Been using the cream for only 15 days and the results are already visible. The skin on my neck feels different—firmer, tighter. Trust me, guys—this is the real deal if you want to look your best without all the fuss.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4QQZ8HQZW_text","label":"gg4QQZ8HQZW_text","default":"<p><strong>Nick A., Texas</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1QwEaURQG_text","label":"gg1QwEaURQG_text","default":"<p>\"I'm 58 and I was considering a neck lift. $8,000 minimum, plus recovery time. Decided to try this first because of the guarantee. Eight weeks later, I'm canceling the consultation. The sagging isn't gone completely, but it's reduced enough that I don't feel like I need surgery anymore. That's worth more than $70.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggotoYeaUAa_text","label":"ggotoYeaUAa_text","default":"<p><strong>Robert M., California</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2CyA24cwm_text","label":"gg2CyA24cwm_text","default":"What to expect, week by week:"},{"type":"html","id":"gggAGkM9rjB_text","label":"gggAGkM9rjB_text","default":"<p>Based on thousands of cases I've tracked, here's the typical progression:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggx3JVJ5n8b_text","label":"ggx3JVJ5n8b_text","default":"<p>Week 1-2:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNVdCO90Ir_text","label":"ggNVdCO90Ir_text","default":"<p>The Foundation&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvyJLS_iR6_text","label":"ggvyJLS_iR6_text","default":"<p>Your skin begins to feel different. Smoother. More hydrated. This is the Hyaluronic Acid establishing a protective moisture matrix while the Retinyl Palmitate begins its slow conversion process.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><i>What you'll notice:</i> Skin feels softer to the touch. Less rough, less dry. People may comment that you \"look rested.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggclpTSyoSG_text","label":"ggclpTSyoSG_text","default":"<p>Week 3-4:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzMwWIPout_text","label":"ggzMwWIPout_text","default":"<p>The Transition&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrUO1nPsKS_text","label":"ggrUO1nPsKS_text","default":"<p>The Retinyl Palmitate is now fully converting to Retinoic Acid within your dermis. Fibroblast activation has begun. New collagen production is underway—you just can't see it yet.<br><br><i>What you'll notice:</i> Skin tone begins to even out. Fine lines appear softer. The texture is visibly improved.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4ozl2Y7_g_text","label":"gg4ozl2Y7_g_text","default":"<p>Week 5-6:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggq3yw4DuJQ_text","label":"ggq3yw4DuJQ_text","default":"<p>The Emergence</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg07ihRwmmu_text","label":"gg07ihRwmmu_text","default":"<p>New collagen fibers are now accumulating in sufficient quantity to begin affecting surface appearance. The scaffolding is being rebuilt.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><i>What you'll notice:</i> Early signs of firming. The jawline may appear slightly more defined. The \"crepe\" texture on the neck begins to smooth.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIG3Zpe_VI_text","label":"ggIG3Zpe_VI_text","default":"<p>Week 7-8:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUJi1XswRj_text","label":"ggUJi1XswRj_text","default":"<p>The Transformation</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQjjX9-kuL_text","label":"ggQjjX9-kuL_text","default":"<p>This is when men typically see dramatic visible change. The collagen matrix has been sufficiently rebuilt to create structural improvement that's obvious in the mirror and in photographs.<br><br><i>What you'll notice:</i> Visible tightening of the neck. Improved jawline definition. Reduction in the \"turkey neck\" appearance. Compliments from people who can't quite identify what's different.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4wz_dJQVq_text","label":"gg4wz_dJQVq_text","default":"<p>Week 9+:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggA-hcE2AkG_text","label":"ggA-hcE2AkG_text","default":"<p>The Maintenance</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg02mqLTMVi_text","label":"gg02mqLTMVi_text","default":"<p>Continued use maintains and builds upon these results. The protective elements prevent degradation while the Retinyl Palmitate continues supporting collagen synthesis.<br><br><i>What you'll notice:</i> Sustained improvement. Some men report continued tightening through month 3-4.</p>"}],
